@startuml
title Lease Manager Conceptual Model

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false

class LeaseManager {
  +acquire()
  +heartbeat(session_id)
  +release(session_id)
  +list()
  +reap_stale()
  +has_live_sessions()
}

class Lease {
  +SESSION_ID
  +DISTRO
  +PID
  +STARTED_AT
  +LAST_SEEN
  +STATE
}

class SharedControlDirectory {
  +sessions/
  +draining
  +enabled
  +lock
}

class SocketGuard {
  +has_active_or_connecting_sockets()
}

class ServiceManager {
  +start()
  +stop()
  +enable()
  +disable()
}

LeaseManager "1" --> "*" Lease : manages
LeaseManager --> SharedControlDirectory : stores state
LeaseManager --> SocketGuard : combines with socket state
ServiceManager --> LeaseManager : asks safe-to-disable
ServiceManager --> SocketGuard : checks ESTAB/SYN-RECV

note right of SocketGuard
ESTAB = active request/response
SYN-RECV = connecting client
TIME-WAIT = ignored for liveness
end note

note bottom of ServiceManager
Uses sudo only for service lifecycle operations.
end note

@enduml
